Name: Average time from 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time to the 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' after 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Minimun time between 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Total time from 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' to 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration APPROVED by ADMINISTRATION' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' Cycle Time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE' for re-submission
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration SUBMITTED by EMPLOYEE'

Name: Total time for cases involving 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to reach 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Minimun resolution time of 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' in cases leading to 'Payment Handled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Payment Handled'

Name: Average time from 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration FINAL_APPROVED by SUPERVISOR'

Name: Total time it takes the 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' to be followed by 'Request Payment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Request Payment'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER' in re-submission cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Declaration REJECTED by BUDGET OWNER' and activity 'Declaration APPROVED by BUDGET OWNER'
